    • Field Detail

      • availability

        public java.lang.String[] availability
        Specifies the availability status for the resulting messages. Multiple values are accepted Enum: Alive, Deleted, Purged

      • conversationId

        public java.lang.Long conversationId
        Specifies the conversation identifier for the resulting messages

      • dateFrom

        public java.lang.String dateFrom
        The start datetime for resulting messages in ISO 8601 format including timezone, for example 2016-03-10T18:07:52.534Z. The default value is dateTo minus 24 hours Format: date-time

      • dateTo

        public java.lang.String dateTo
        The end datetime for resulting messages in ISO 8601 format including timezone, for example 2016-03-10T18:07:52.534Z. The default value is current time Format: date-time

      • direction

        public java.lang.String[] direction
        The direction for the resulting messages. If not specified, both inbound and outbound messages are returned. Multiple values are accepted Enum: Inbound, Outbound

      • distinctConversations

        public java.lang.Boolean distinctConversations
        If 'True', then the latest messages per every conversation ID are returned

      • messageType

        public java.lang.String[] messageType
        The type of the resulting messages. If not specified, all messages without message type filtering are returned. Multiple values are accepted Enum: Fax, SMS, VoiceMail, Pager, Text

      • readStatus

        public java.lang.String[] readStatus
        The read status for the resulting messages. Multiple values are accepted Enum: Read, Unread

      • page

        public java.lang.Long page
        Indicates the page number to retrieve. Only positive number values are accepted Default: 1

      • perPage

        public java.lang.Long perPage
        Indicates the page size (number of items) Default: 100

      • phoneNumber

        public java.lang.String phoneNumber
        The phone number. If specified, messages are returned for this particular phone number only
